This is Openradius module for Retransmission Hints.
For simple test: 
    cd example/
    gcc radclient.c -o radclient
    ./multi_radclient -r path_to_multi_radclient/examples/radclient
this test is echo-radclient which return the same package. For example,
you may use path_to_multi_radclient/examples/input packages.
